title: Ep. - 188 - BEHIND THE SCENES OF BEHIND THE MUSIC ON VH1
description:
VH1’s biography series Behind The Music landed the biggest names in music covering every dark detail of their rise to (and sometimes fall from) the top. Artists including Madonna, Milli Vanilli, Metallica, Ricky Martin, Whitney Houston, TLC, Usher, Jennifer Lopez, and Shania Twain detailed parts of their lives, many until then unknown to the public. Over 250 episodes they documented some of music’s greatest artists and stories. Executive George Moll explains how the show was developed, intricacies of filming, behind the scenes stories, and whether the show has plans to come back. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
